{
  "_comment": [
    "Profile P3 -- the A-GRA Core MMS (uci_mms_conversion_plan.md §5, row",
    "'P3 -- full Core MMS'). Root list is every unique Message Name in",
    "Table 3-1 of ref/a-gra-main/Documentation/ASK 5.0a MA L1 Compliance",
    "Document.pdf (all four interfaces -- C2, MS, P2P, VI -- and all MUC",
    "tags, Core and optional alike), resolved to top-level *element* names",
    "against the pinned agra_5_0a drop (the MT suffix in the compliance",
    "document belongs to the element's complexType, not the element itself",
    "-- e.g. table row 'ActionActivityMT' is XSD element 'ActionActivity'",
    "of type 'ActionActivityMT'; a few names carry the suffix as a literal",
    "'_MT', e.g. 'DLZ' -> type 'DLZ_MT', resolved the same way).",
    "",
    "343 unique message names parsed from the table (~327 in the a-gra",
    "standard review's approximate count; this list is the direct table",
    "parse against the schema's own element/type map, not a re-derivation",
    "of the review's estimate, so the two are not expected to match",
    "exactly). All 20 profile P2 roots are contained in this set.",
    "",
    "Per doc/plans/PYRAMID/uci_mms_conversion_plan.md §5/Phase 5, P3 is",
    "'Not scheduled; only under a real compliance tasking'. This manifest",
    "and the CMake option gating its generated codec/bindings",
    "(PYRAMID_ENABLE_AGRA_P3, OFF by default) exist so the proto tree can",
    "be produced and built on demand without that tasking having happened",
    "-- no MA L1 compliance claim, no offline fidelity ladder (goldens,",
    "round-trips, malformed-input negatives) or live interop evidence has",
    "been run against it, unlike P1/P2. Do not grow or shrink this list",
    "without re-parsing Table 3-1 and re-running xsd2proto.py --check.",
    "",
    "Generated into pim/uci_generated_p3/ rather than pim/uci_generated/:",
    "closure_report.json and wire_names.json live at the <out>/<drop>/",
    "root, and P3 shares the agra_5_0a drop with the already-checked-in",
    "P2 tree under pim/uci_generated/agra_5_0a/ -- a shared --out root",
    "would have overwritten P2's sidecar files despite the different",
    "proto_package.",
    "",
    "The usable contract (data model plus per-interface component service",
    "protos with pubsub/rpc port-grammar annotations) is the seam at",
    "pim/agra_p3_seam/, generated by pim/gen_interaction_seam.py from",
    "this manifest, the converted tree, and the Table 3-1",
    "interface/direction data in p3_agra_core_mms_interfaces.json."
  ],
